        "title": {
          "en": "Byte-Level Interface Proposed for Cross-Tokenizer LLM Distillation",
          "zh": "字节级接口方案助力跨分词器LLM蒸馏"
        },
        "tl_dr": {
          "en": "A recent arXiv paper introduces Byte-Level Distillation (BLD), a simple and effective baseline enabling cross-tokenizer LLM distillation via a byte-level interface to solve a largely unsolved problem.",
          "zh": "一篇最新的arXiv论文提出字节级蒸馏（BLD）方法，这是一个简单而有效的基线，通过字节级接口实现了跨分词器LLM蒸馏，解决了此前一个悬而未决的问题。"
        },
        "key_takeaways": {
          "en": [
            "Cross-tokenizer distillation (CTD) involves transferring knowledge between language models that use different tokenizers.",
            "Existing CTD approaches rely on heuristic strategies for vocabulary alignment, introducing considerable complexity.",
            "Byte-Level Distillation (BLD) enables CTD by operating at a common byte-level interface, presented as a simple and effective baseline."
          ],
          "zh": [
            "跨分词器蒸馏（CTD）是指在采用不同分词器的语言模型之间进行知识迁移。",
            "现有CTD方法依赖启发式策略对不匹配的词汇表进行对齐，引入了相当大的复杂性。",
            "字节级蒸馏（BLD）通过在通用的字节级接口上操作来实现CTD，被提出为一个简单而有效的基线。"
          ]
        },
        "impact": {
          "en": "This method addresses a largely unsolved problem in transferring knowledge between language models with different tokenizers. Its simplicity and effectiveness could improve the interoperability and efficiency of LLM knowledge transfer across diverse architectures.",
          "zh": "该方法解决了在不同分词器语言模型之间进行知识迁移的一个主要未解决问题。其简单性和有效性可能提高LLM知识在不同架构间转移的互操作性和效率。"
        },
        "source": "arXiv CS.CL",
        "link": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2604.07466"
      },
